text: Fever is the eighth studio album by Australian singer Kylie Minogue. It was released on 1 October 2001 by Parlophone Records. The album contains four singles, "Can't Get You Out of My Head", "In Your Eyes", "Love at First Sight", and "Come into My World". "Come into My World" won Minogue won a Grammy Award for Best Dance Recording, her first Grammy. Minogue embarked on her KylieFever2002 tour to promote the album. == Track listing == == Other websites == *Fever on Kylie Minogue's official website Category:2001 albums Category:Kylie Minogue albums Category:Dance-pop albums
